  "text": "We conduct two set of experiments: (1) Single database experiment involving SMIC and CASME II with their original estimated emotion classes, and CASME II and SAMM with the reorganized objective classes I-V. (2) Cross-database experiments involving SMIC, CASME II , and SAMM following the Guidelines of the 1st MEGC [CITATION_1] and the 2nd MEGC [CITATION_2] .",
